<section id="Section574794">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>opportunities</primary>
      <secondary>master list of</secondary>
    </indexterm>List Opportunities</title>
  <para>To access the list of Opportunities, select the "List Opportunities"
  option. The following screen will appear.</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/opportunityList.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Opportunities Master List</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When reviewing the Opportunities list, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <note>
    <para>The system-defined default filter on the Opportunities list shows
    all active Opportunities.</para>
  </note>
  <xi:include href="../widgets/parameterwidget.xml" xpointer="parameterwidget"
              xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Opportunities</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists available Opportunities, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <xi:include href="../widgets/fliterManager.xml" xpointer="filterManager"
              xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
</section>
